{"id": "0482-containment", "word": "containment", "tweet1": {"text": "SCP secret laboratory is soooo funnn omg, I didn't even have this much fun in containment breach", "tokens": ["SCP", "secret", "laboratory", "is", "soooo", "funnn", "omg", ",", "I", "didn't", "even", "have", "this", "much", "fun", "in", "containment", "breach"], "token_idx": 16, "text_start": 78, "text_end": 89, "date": "2019-03"}, "tweet2": {"text": "Soooo the word for containment in French is \"confinement\". You English speaking people should know that if you see \"Confinement global\", it doesn't mean that a lot of people are going to give birth in the same time.", "tokens": ["Soooo", "the", "word", "for", "containment", "in", "French", "is", "\"", "confinement", "\"", ".", "You", "English", "speaking", "people", "should", "know", "that", "if", "you", "see", "\"", "Confinement", "global", "\"", ",", "it", "doesn't", "mean", "that", "a", "lot", "of", "people", "are", "going", "to", "give", "birth", "in", "the", "same", "time", "."], "token_idx": 4, "text_start": 19, "text_end": 30, "date": "2020-03"}}
