{"id": "0484-containment", "word": "containment", "tweet1": {"text": "By managing resources and finances well, cost containment limits unnecessary expenditures and unproductive investments. In healthcare, this may lead to an effective reallocation of finances so that beneficial, long-term investments can be made. #HealthcareEconomics", "tokens": ["By", "managing", "resources", "and", "finances", "well", ",", "cost", "containment", "limits", "unnecessary", "expenditures", "and", "unproductive", "investments", ".", "In", "healthcare", ",", "this", "may", "lead", "to", "an", "effective", "reallocation", "of", "finances", "so", "that", "beneficial", ",", "long-term", "investments", "can", "be", "made", ".", "#HealthcareEconomics"], "token_idx": 8, "text_start": 46, "text_end": 57, "date": "2019-03"}, "tweet2": {"text": "i dont think watching containment at 4am is gonna make me feel better ðŸ¤¡", "tokens": ["i", "dont", "think", "watching", "containment", "at", "4am", "is", "gonna", "make", "me", "feel", "better", "ðŸ¤¡"], "token_idx": 4, "text_start": 22, "text_end": 33, "date": "2020-03"}}
{"id": "0485-containment", "word": "containment", "tweet1": {"text": "Proper containment of an area that #asbestos is being removed from is of the utmost importance. When removing it, the fibrous particles float in the air, and into the lungs of those not wearing proper equipment, or prepped with proper containment. Definitely not a DIY project!", "tokens": ["Proper", "containment", "of", "an", "area", "that", "#asbestos", "is", "being", "removed", "from", "is", "of", "the", "utmost", "importance", ".", "When", "removing", "it", ",", "the", "fibrous", "particles", "float", "in", "the", "air", ",", "and", "into", "the", "lungs", "of", "those", "not", "wearing", "proper", "equipment", ",", "or", "prepped", "with", "proper", "containment", ".", "Definitely", "not", "a", "DIY", "project", "!"], "token_idx": 1, "text_start": 7, "text_end": 18, "date": "2019-03"}, "tweet2": {"text": "It's unfortunate that countries, especially the West, are so reactive towards the containment and detection of coronavirus. To see how the world turned a blind eye on China until the reality hit them hard is disappointing. Hope everyone and the world get well real soon.", "tokens": ["It's", "unfortunate", "that", "countries", ",", "especially", "the", "West", ",", "are", "so", "reactive", "towards", "the", "containment", "and", "detection", "of", "coronavirus", ".", "To", "see", "how", "the", "world", "turned", "a", "blind", "eye", "on", "China", "until", "the", "reality", "hit", "them", "hard", "is", "disappointing", ".", "Hope", "everyone", "and", "the", "world", "get", "well", "real", "soon", "."], "token_idx": 14, "text_start": 82, "text_end": 93, "date": "2020-03"}}
